                        <additions>
                            <list> 
                                
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#46v"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                                        A note giving the name of one  <persName type="donor" ref="PRS11650MahtamaKrestos"></persName>,
                                        who bought this manuscript for a church of <persName type="tabot" ref="PRS7049Michael">St Michael</persName>.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ ፡ ዛማኅተመ ፡ ክርስ ቶስ ።  ዘአጥረዮ ፡ በነዋዩ ፡ ለታበተ ፡ ሚካኤል ።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#147v"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                                        A note, in the same hand as the manuscript, stating that it belonged to one 
                                        <persName type="owner" ref="PRS11651TaklaGiyorgis"></persName>.
                                        
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ለዝንቱ  መጽሐፈ ፡ ወንጌል ፡ ቅዱስ ፡ ዘአጥ ረዮ ፡ በንዋዩ ፡ ተክለ ፡ ጊዮርጊስ ፡ ክመ ፡ ይኩኖ ፡ ተዝካረ ፡ 
                                        በዕለተ ፡ ክርስትስ ፡ ይጽሐ ፍ ፡ ስሞ ፡ ውስተ ፡ መጽሐፈ ፡ ሕይወት ፡ ዘኢይደመሰስ ፡ በክመ ፡ ጸሐፈ ፡ ዮሐንስ ፡ ስመ ፡ ረድኡ ፡ አብሮኮሮስ ፡ 
                                        እግዚአብሔር ፡ ንጉሥ ፡ ወይክፍሎ ፡ ኃዲረ ፡ ውስት ፡ መካነ ፡ ዛሕን ፡ ወመርስ ፡ አሜን ። etc.</q>
                                </item>           
                            
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#147v"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                                        Subsequently the ms belonged to one <persName type="owner" ref="PRS11652Matewos">Mātewos</persName> and his son   
                                        <persName type="owner" ref="PRS11653KenfaM">ʾabbā Kǝnfa Mikāʾel</persName>.
                                        
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ ፡ ዛማቴዎስ ፡ ወለውሉዱ ፡ አባ ፡ ክንፈ ፡ ሚካኤል ። </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                
                                <item xml:id="a4">
                                    <locus target="#148r"/>
                                    <desc type="PoemSalam">
                                        Salām to various saints, in an old hand.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም ፡ ለዮሐንስ ፡ ዛይሴሰይ ፡ አሕማላት ።  ...</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a5">
                                    <locus target="#148v"/>
                                    <desc type="Genealogy">
                                        A genealogy, <q xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ ፡ ልደ ቱ ፡ ለእነማይ  ...</q>, 
                                        ending with the name of the writer, <persName type="author" ref="PRS11654EsbaGiyorgis"/>, 
                                        followed by a continuation, <q xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ ፡ ሊደቱ ፡ ለ፱ልጀ ፡ (sic) እነማይ  ...</q>.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a6">
                                    <locus target="#149r"/>
                                    <desc type="Genealogy">
                                        Another genealogy, <q xml:lang="gez">ወበዋትይሂ ፡ መጽሐፈ ፡ ልደቱ ፡ ለነመራጌ ፡  ...</q>, 
                                        ending with the name of the writer, <persName type="author" ref="PRS11655WakaDengel"/>.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                                
                                <item xml:id="a7">
                                    <locus target="#149r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                                        An extract from a homily (dǝrsān) on the holy Eucharist (qʷǝrbān) and on the last hours of our Lord.
                                    </desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                
                            </list>
